        </figure><h3 class="title" data-click-tracking="genericClickCbsNews" data-omniture-track-data='{"clickProperty": "Post-REM Block|Article-1-Headline"}'>Arrest in prosecutor's murder after tipster contacts reporter</h3>

        <p class="dek" data-click-tracking="genericClickCbsNews" data-omniture-track-data='{"clickProperty": "Post-REM Block|Article-1-Body"}'>
A 70-year-old man has been arrested in the 1999 slaying of a Colorado prosecutor following a CBS Denver investigation</p>
            </a>
</li>

                            
                                                



    
    
